@romansharf is a serious guy and has spent over A BILLION dollars on watches., a lot of people talk big talk on the watch subject but they are really Mickey Mouse compared to him.

You can find the full video on our YouTube, part 2 to this interview will come soon.

You guys voted for Death Row, did he?

Some people are getting upset about what we do to raise our brand and quality higher. I have a lot to say to those people and I hope for their sake they never hear me say it. 

Live chat on TraxNYC.com
